<div class="title">A Lot Like the Truth</div>
<div class="substance">4-Fluoroamphetamine & 2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <A HREF="exp.cgi?A=ShowAuthor&ID=7">Zam</A></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Zam. "A Lot Like the Truth: An Experience with 4-Fluoroamphetamine & 2C-B (exp54633)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 17, 2006. erowid.org/exp/54633</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td><a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=ShowAuthor&ID=7"><img src="/experiences/images/authors/author_logo_default_grn.gif" alt="author logo" align="right" border="0" /></a>
